This template displays an external link to a page for a game designer at the [[BoardGameGeek]] website.

== Usage ==
Unnamed parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>|<var>ID3</var>|<var>NAME3</var>}}

Named parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>|name{{=}}<var>NAME</var>}}

Using [[维基数据|Wikidata]] property {{property|P3505}}:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|name{{=}}<var>NAME</var>}}

== Example ==
''Usage in the article {{tsl|en|Klaus Teuber||Klaus Teuber}}, with article name as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|11}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}11}}

''Usage with name parameter as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|11|Klaus Teuber}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}11|name{{=}}Klaus Teuber}}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|11|Klaus Teuber}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id=11|name=Klaus Teuber}}

''URLs:''
: <kbd>[https://www.boardgamegeek.com/person/11 https://www.boardgamegeek.com/person/{{hilite|11}}]</kbd> (used in template)
: <kbd>[https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgamedesigner/11/klaus-teuber https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgamedesigner/{{hilite|11}}/klaus-teuber]</kbd> (redirect at website)

